title: Windows 10 Pro X64 6in1 OEM MULTi-12 Aug 2015 {Generation2}
description:
* Windows 10 Pro X64 6in1 OEM MULTi-12 Aug 2015 {Generation2} 


[ RELEASE INFO ]


* This release contains one ISO [SOURCE ISO] and eleven exe-files.

* All exe-files are created from WINDOWS 10 PRO RTM BUILD 10240 en-US
* This is done with SmartVersion, a program that calculates the 
* difference between two files (one of which is used as the source) 
* and then creates an svf-file based on that difference.
 
* Hashes attached in a separate .txt 

[ DOWNLOAD INFO ]

* Download the Source ISO and preferred language.exe

* If you want en-US then just download the SOURCE ISO
 
* Run the exe-file in the same folder as the SOURCE ISO.
* This will extract the ISO in the selected language. 

[ EDITIONS INCLUDED ]

* Windows 10 Pro
* Windows 10 Home
* Windows 10 Enterprise

* Windows 10 Pro		OEM-Activated
* Windows 10 Home		OEM-Activated
* Windows 10 Enterprise		OEM-Activated

* OEM (Original Equipment Manufacturer) will automatically
* activate original version installed by Manufacturer. 
	         
[ LANGUAGES & SOURCES ]

* da-DK [ Danish ]
* de-DE [ German ]
* en-US [ English ]
* es-ES [ Spanish ]
* fi-FI [ Finnish ]
* fr-FR [ French ]
* it-IT [ Italian ]
* nb-NO [ Norwegian ]
* nl-NL [ Dutch ]
* pt-BR [ Brazilian ]
* pt-PT [ Portuguese ]
* sv-SE [ Swedish ]

[ SOURCE ISO ]

* Win10.X64.en-US.iso - Size: 3,89GB

[ EXE-FILES ]

* Win10.X64.da-DK.exe - Size:  225MB
* Win10.X64.de-DE.exe - Size:  232MB
* Win10.X64.es-ES.exe - Size:  232MB
* Win10.X64.fi-FI.exe - Size:  226MB
* Win10.X64.fr-FR.exe - Size:  233MB
* Win10.X64.it-IT.exe - Size:  230MB
* Win10.X64.nb-NO.exe - Size:  227MB
* Win10.X64.nl-NL.exe - Size:  230MB
* Win10.X64.pt-BR.exe - Size:  234MB
* Win10.X64.pt-PT.exe - Size:  222MB
* Win10.X64.sv-SE.exe - Size:  227MB

[ COMMENTS & ACTIVATION INFO ]

* Keys for all Editions included in a separate .txt
* Activator: Microsoft Toolkit v2.5.3 

* For instructions on how to activate,
* please see the included video
* Potential False Positive Virus Alarm.

[ INSTALLATION & INFORMATION ]

* Create bootable USB (highly recommended) with Rufus,
* (attached) or burn to DVD at slow speed.

* Credits:
* milrob and stevie-boy for continued support and help with user questions.

* Hope you will enjoy this release!

* Regards,
* Generation2 @ KAT & TPB
